query:
UPDATE event
            SET modification_date_time = now(),
                program_id = $2,
                event_name = $3,
                priority = $4,
                targets = $5,
                report_descriptors = $6,
                payload_descriptors = $7,
                interval_period = $8,
                intervals = $9
            WHERE id = $1
            RETURNING
                id,
                created_date_time,
                modification_date_time,
                program_id,
                event_name,
                priority,
                targets as "targets:Vec<Target>",
                report_descriptors,
                payload_descriptors,
                interval_period,
                intervals
